{"_id":"GTgnAdv00001trnX","name":"Advanced Training","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Chosen Skill Rank 5","description":"This character has pushed mastery of a certain Skill beyond what most would consider natural.\n\nChoose a Skill that meets the requirement. When performing a duel using the chosen Skill, increase the final duel total by +1.\n\nMay be taken multiple times; each time a different Skill must be chosen."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnArm00002trnX","name":"Armor Training","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"None","description":"This character has learned to wear armor without impeding her movements.\n\nReduce the penalty to Defense from wearing armor by 1 (minimum 0).\n\nMay be taken multiple times."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":100000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnBck00003walX","name":"Back to the Wall","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Tenacity 2 or higher","description":"When there's nowhere to run, this character hunkers down and prepares for the worst.\n\nWhen within 1 yard of a wall or solid object at least as tall as the character, she gains +1 Defense."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":200000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnBpv00004valX","name":"Better Part of Valor","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Tenacity -1 or lower","description":"When the going gets tough, it's probably better to go the other way.\n\nThis character's Charge Aspect becomes \"--\" (cannot take the Charge Action), but gains +2 to Walk Aspect."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":300000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnBli00005ignX","name":"Blissful Ignorance","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Cunning -1 or lower","description":"This character is unaware of frightening details around her, which occasionally works in her favor.\n\nWhen this character fails a Horror Duel:\n- If it is her turn: her current Action immediately fails, but she does not become Paralyzed.\n- If it is not her turn: she becomes Slow instead of Paralyzed."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":400000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnCal00006shtX","name":"Call Shot","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Fated","description":"This character's aim is quite good.\n\nChoose a Skill. When generating a Critical Effect with an attack using the chosen Skill, she may discard a card to change the Critical Effect's suit to the suit of the discarded card.\n\nMay be taken multiple times; each time a different Skill must be chosen."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":500000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnClm00007colX","name":"Calm And Collected","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Speed -1 or lower","description":"This character has learned that rushing leads to mistakes.\n\nThis character adds +1 to the value of any Focused Condition she receives, to a maximum of Focused +3."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":600000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnClr00008ordX","name":"Clear Orders","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Leadership 3 or higher","description":"This character gives orders that are clear and concise.\n\nWhen taking the Order Action to give commands to subordinate characters, this character may Cheat Fate for those characters."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":700000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnCmb00009rdgX","name":"Combat Reading","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Cunning 1 or higher","description":"This character reads a target during combat and strikes at openings others might not see.\n\nWhen making disengaging strikes, add Scrutiny Skill ranks to the final duel total."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":800000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnCnt00010splX","name":"Counterspell","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Counter-Spelling 3 or higher","description":"Training in Counter-Spelling has given this character an intuitive ability to resist magic.\n\nWhen this character is targeted by an enemy's Magical Action, the enemy loses all suits associated with their Magical Skill."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":900000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnCrt00011strX","name":"Critical Strike","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Close Combat or Ranged Combat Skill 3 or higher","description":"A skilled attacker deals more damage than a common thug.\n\nChoose a Skill that meets the requirement. All attacks with the chosen Skill gain the following Trigger:\n\nR Critical Strike: When damaging, deal +1 damage per R in the final duel total.\n\nMay be taken multiple times; each time a different Skill must be chosen."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1000000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnCyn00012cynX","name":"Cynic","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Charm -1 or lower","description":"If it sounds too good to be true, this character gets suspicious.\n\nGains + on any duel made to resist deception (including Deceive and Pick Pocket Challenges, as well as the Trick Action)."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1100000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnDfp00013proX","name":"Defensive Protocols","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Leadership 3 or higher","description":"This character organizes subordinates into defensive formations with little effort.\n\nSubordinate characters within a6 of this character may flip cards when attacked, in the same manner as a Fated character."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1200000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnDck00014covX","name":"Duck and Cover","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Evade 3 or higher","description":"This character knows how to avoid flying shrapnel and roaring flames.\n\nGains the following ability:\nBlast Resistant +1: Reduce all damage from pulse (p) and blast (b) effects by +1 (minimum 1)."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1300000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnFlk00015wrsX","name":"Flick of the Wrist","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Might -1 or lower","description":"This character is precise where others rely on brute strength.\n\nWhen making a Melee or Pugilism attack, may substitute Grace for Might when calculating Acting value."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1400000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnGvg00016gftX","name":"Governor's Gift","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Charm 1 or higher","description":"Some people just have a way with members of a certain gender.\n\nChoose male or female. Gains + on Bewitch and Scrutiny duels made against members of the chosen gender."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1500000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnGtf00017fatX","name":"Great Fate","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Fated","description":"Fate smiles upon this character, allowing her to manipulate destiny more frequently.\n\nWhen drawing her Control Hand at the end of the Prologue, draw one additional card.\n\nMay be taken multiple times; effects stack."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1600000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnGrs00018atkX","name":"Gruesome Attack","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Close Combat or Ranged Combat Skill 3 or higher","description":"Combat is a dangerous thing, especially when this character is involved.\n\nChoose a Skill. All Critical Effect flips from attacks using the chosen Skill receive +.\n\nMay be taken multiple times; each time a different Skill must be chosen."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1700000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnGrf00019grfX","name":"Gruff","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Charm -1 or lower","description":"This character speaks plainly, making it difficult for others to discern her true intentions.\n\nGains + to Deceive and Intimidate Challenges."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1800000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnHbl00020atkX","name":"Hobbling Attack","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Close Combat or Ranged Combat Skill 3 or higher","description":"This character places attacks in just the right spot to slow her target down.\n\nChoose a Skill. All attacks with the chosen Skill gain the following Trigger:\n\nC Hobble: After succeeding, the target gains the following Condition for the remainder of Dramatic Time: \"Hobbled: This character may only declare one Movement General Action per turn and may not declare the Run Action.\"\n\nMay be taken multiple times; each time a different Skill must be chosen."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1900000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnHns00021hnsX","name":"Honest","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Cunning -1 or lower","description":"Others can see this character has an honest nature; she doesn't have to try to earn trust.\n\nGains + to all Convince and Leadership Duels."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2000000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnImp00022masX","name":"Imposing Mass","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Grace -1 or lower","description":"This character uses her physical size to great advantage in combat.\n\nGains + to disengaging strikes and to any Impose Action she takes."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2100000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnLms00023shwX","name":"Let Me Show You","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Leadership 3 or higher","description":"This character has a natural affinity for teaching others.\n\nSpend 15 minutes and discard a Twist Card to explain how one of her General Talents works. The other character may then discard a Twist Card to gain that General Talent for the rest of the day.\n\n- The taught character must still meet all physical prerequisites of the Talent.\n- Talents with requirements of Invested, Stitched, or Twisted cannot be taught.\n\nUpdated Talent -- originally appeared in Into the Steam."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2200000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnOpn00024fgtX","name":"Open Hand Fighting","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Melee 3 or higher","description":"Having a free hand can have its advantages in combat.\n\nIf wielding a Melee weapon with nothing in the other hand when making a successful disengaging strike, the character may choose to have the disengaging strike deal damage to the target."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2300000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnPrd00025wpnX","name":"Paired Weapons","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Close Combat or Ranged Combat Skill 3 or higher","description":"This character effectively wields two weapons at the same time.\n\nChoose a Skill. When wielding two weapons of the chosen type (one in each hand), gain + to all attacks made with either weapon. Despite fighting with two weapons:\n- Only a single attack flip is made.\n- Only one weapon deals damage; the second provides the bonus to hit.\n- If wielding two Ranged Combat weapons, expend one round of ammunition from each.\n\nMay be taken multiple times; each time a different Skill must be chosen."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2400000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnPln00026spkX","name":"Plain-Spoken","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Intellect -1 or lower","description":"This character is good at saying difficult truths efficiently without flowery language.\n\nGains + to Social Duels made during Dramatic Time."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2500000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnPly00027lngX","name":"Polyglot","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Intellect 1 or higher","description":"This character has a natural knack for languages.\n\nUpon taking this Talent, choose two languages not already spoken and learn them. When conversing with another character in their native non-English language, gain + to Barter and Bewitch duels."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2600000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnQks00028stdX","name":"Quick Study","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Intellect 1 or higher","description":"Some people just learn quickly from watching others.\n\nDuring the Epilogue Skill Advancement, may instead advance in any Skill not yet possessed rather than the FM-presented options, provided the character witnessed a friendly character succeed at that Skill during the session."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2700000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnRsh00029rshX","name":"Rush","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Speed 1 or higher","description":"This character is adept at charging headlong into combat.\n\nIncreases Charge Aspect by +1.\n\nMay be taken multiple times; effects stack."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2800000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnScs00030splX","name":"Secretive Spellcasting","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Magical Theory","description":"This character has learned to hide spellcasting within the trappings of the Thalarian Doctrine.\n\nWhen casting a Spell or Manifested Power, may discard a card to make her Magical Theory appear to be the Thalarian Doctrine to detection attempts."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2900000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnSzd00031dayX","name":"Seize the Day","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Grace -1 or lower","description":"This character overcompensates for awkwardness by ensuring the fight ends quickly.\n\nGains + to Initiative flips."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3000000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnShs00032stdX","name":"Shot Studies","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Shotgun 3 or higher","description":"Shotguns are second nature to this character.\n\nIf this character has the Focused Condition and fires a shotgun loaded with slug ammunition, multiply the shotgun's range by x10."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3100000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnShv00033asdX","name":"Shove Aside","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Might 1 or higher","description":"This character can barrel through others with little resistance.\n\nThis character can move through characters with a Height lower than her own without being impeded. Such characters cannot make disengaging strikes against this character."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3200000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnShg00034offX","name":"Shrug Off","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Resilience -1 or lower","description":"This character is so accustomed to minor pains she can ignore them entirely.\n\nGains the following Tactical Action:\n(0) Shrug Off: Discard a Twist Card to end a Condition affecting this character."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3300000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnSps00035sklX","name":"Specialized Skill","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Fatemaster Character or 2 or more completed Destiny Steps","description":"This character has honed a specific skill, allowing her to perform tricks with little effort.\n\nChoose a Skill and a suit. Add the chosen suit to that Skill's value.\n\nMay be taken multiple times; each time a different Skill must be chosen."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3400000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnSpt00036toxX","name":"Specialized Toxins","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Alchemistry 2 or higher","description":"This character knows the perfect poison for a specific kind of creature.\n\nChoose one of the following Characteristics: Living, Construct, Undead, Spirit, or Nightmare. When this character performs an Action or declares a Trigger that would give a target with the chosen Characteristic the Poison Condition:\n- The effect applies even if the target is not Living.\n- The target gains an additional Poison +1 for each chosen Characteristic it possesses.\n\nMay be taken multiple times; each time a different Characteristic must be chosen."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3500000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnSpd00037ldgX","name":"Speed Loading","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Chosen Skill Rank 2 or higher","description":"This character knows how to quickly reload her weapon in combat.\n\nChoose Long Arms, Pistols, Shotguns, or Heavy Weapons. The character gains the following Trigger on any attack Action using the chosen Skill:\n\nR Speed Loading: If this weapon's Reload AP cost is 2 or lower, reload this weapon."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3600000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnStm00038chgX","name":"Steam-Powered Charge","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Character must be a Construct or possess one or more pneumatic limbs","description":"When this character charges, she pushes her pneumatic limbs to their limits and hits like a steam locomotive.\n\nWhen declaring the Charge Action, she may choose to make a single (1) AP or (2) AP Close Combat attack instead of two (1) AP Close Combat attacks.\n- If she makes a single (1) AP attack: deals +1 damage and knocks the target Prone on success."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3700000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnSty00039styX","name":"Sturdy","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"None","description":"This character can push her body to endure wounds that would leave larger people incapacitated.\n\nGains +2 Wounds.\n\nMay be taken multiple times. Each additional time: gains +1 Wound."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3800000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnSrf00040ftdX","name":"Sure-Footed","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Speed -1 or lower","description":"This character might not move quickly, but she's hard to budge.\n\nWhen this character is pushed or moved by an effect, she may apply her Speed Aspect as a penalty (in yards) to the distance pushed or moved."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3900000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnTnw00041warX","name":"Tenacious Warrior","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Resilience 2 or higher","description":"This rugged character ignores the worst parts of most attacks.\n\nWhen an enemy makes a successful attack against this character and declares a Trigger, this character may discard a card. If she does, the Trigger has no effect on her (though the Trigger may still affect other characters, and she still suffers all other effects of the attack normally)."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4000000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnThp00042posX","name":"Threatening Posture","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Intimidate 3 or higher","description":"This character is so threatening that her presence distracts opponents from attacking her allies.\n\nEnemies engaged with this character suffer - on Close Combat attacks made against targets other than her, unless those targets also possess this Talent."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4100000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnTrk00043shtX","name":"Tricky Shot","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Chosen Skill Rank 2 or higher","description":"This character is highly adept at pulling off tricky shots in a variety of conditions.\n\nChoose a Ranged Combat Skill. While making an attack with the chosen Skill, this character may ignore one -."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4200000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnTwf00044fatX","name":"Twisted Fates","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Fated","description":"This character can bend luck to her will more often than most.\n\nChoose one card in the character's Twist deck and permanently increase its value by 1 (maximum value 13).\n\nMay be taken multiple times."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4300000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnUns00045asmX","name":"Unassuming","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Might -1 or lower","description":"A lifetime of dealing with those stronger than her has taught this character how to present a calm manner and blend in.\n\nGains + to any duels made to avoid being noticed in a group or angering someone."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4400000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnUmc00046cnfX","name":"Undermine Confidence","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Resilience -1 or lower","description":"Sometimes it's better to talk big and let nervousness set in slowly.\n\nGains + to all Intimidate Challenges made during Narrative Time."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4500000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnUna00047accX","name":"Unequaled Accuracy","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Magical or Ranged Combat Skill 2 or higher","description":"This character has an unequaled sense of timing when shooting into a chaotic fight.\n\nChoose a Skill that meets the requirement. This character does not randomize her target when firing into an engagement using the chosen Skill."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4600000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnWom00048mslX","name":"Wall of Muscle","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Resilience 1 or higher","description":"This character is both tall and wide, and she knows how to use her size to her advantage.\n\n- Increase this character's Height to 3.\n- Increase the range of all reach (y) weapons wielded by this character by 1 yard (maximum 3 yards).\n\nIf taken after character creation, the character must have justification for this growth."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4700000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTgnWoa00049ageX","name":"Will of Ages","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-teal.webp","system":{"pursuit":"general","requirements":"Counter-Spelling 3 or higher","description":"This character has learned how to protect multiple characters from harmful magic.\n\nWhen using Magical Shielding, she may shield a number of additional friendly characters (including herself) equal to her Tenacity."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4800000,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
